 clay; L. masc. n. <em>sinus</em> bend; N.L. masc. n. <em>Pelosinus</em> a curved organism from clay).</s></p><p class="description"><s>Cells are Gram-negative, motile, slightly curved rods.</s><s>Spore-forming.</s><s>Sporangia are distinctly swollen.</s><s>Obligately anaerobic.</s><s>Mesophilic.</s><s>Does not produce acetate from H<sub>2</sub>+CO<sub>2</sub>.</s><s>Fermentative.</s><s>Uses a variety of fermentative substrates, but does not ferment glycerol.</s><s>The type species is <em>Pelosinus fermentans</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>